# 🚀 Intelligent Notification System using n8n

## 📌 Overview

This project is built using n8n to automate and manage notifications intelligently.
It filters important messages and reduces unnecessary noise by using workflow automation and AI-based logic.

---

## 🔥 Features

* 📩 Smart message filtering
* ⚡ Automated workflows
* 🤖 AI-powered responses (optional integration with Claude)
* 🔔 Priority-based notifications
* ⏱️ Real-time processing

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* n8n (Workflow Automation)
* REST APIs
* Webhooks
* AI Integration (Claude API - optional)

